title: Ground News - Commissioner reviews facilities at Catholic Church, Holy Family Hospital
text:
Summary by The News Rawalpindi : Commissioner Rawalpindi Division Liaquat Ali Chatta here on Thursday visited the Catholic Church in Holy Family Hospital and reviewed the facilities.During the visit, the Commissioner also checked the arrangements for the separate entrance of the church.
